<h1 id="adjustment-of-the-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate" sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="26">Adjustment of the asset retirement obligation estimate</h1>

[!include[banner](../../includes/banner.md)]
<p sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="30">For Japan, the initial estimate of the asset retirement obligations (ARO) can be adjusted.</p>
<p sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="34">Use this procedure to learn how to adjust the ARO amount.</p>
<p sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="38">To complete this procedure, the Fixed Assets configuration key must be selected.</p>
<p sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="42">This task was created using the demo data company JPMF.</p>
<h2 id="adjust-the-aro-estimate" sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="45">Adjust the ARO estimate</h2>
<ol sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="46">
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="46">Go to Fixed assets &gt; Asset retirement obligations &gt; Fixed assets.</li>
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="47">In the list, find and select the desired record.</li>
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="48">On the Action Pane, click Fixed asset.</li>
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="49">Click Asset retirement obligation.</li>
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="50">Click Upward to open the drop dialog.
<ul sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="51">
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="51">You can also click Downward for minus adjustment.</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="52">In the Transaction date field, enter the date on which to post the adjustment amount.</li>
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="53">In the Upward field, enter the amount of adjustment.</li>
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="54">Click OK.</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="post-the-adjustment" sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="56">Post the adjustment</h2>
<ol sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="57">
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="57">Go to Fixed assets &gt; Asset retirement obligations &gt; Fixed assets journal.</li>
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="58">Click New.</li>
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="59">In the Name field, type a value.</li>
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="60">Click Save.</li>
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="61">Click Lines.</li>
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="62">Click Proposals.</li>
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="63">Click Capitalized asset retirement obligation.</li>
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="64">In the To date field, enter a date.</li>
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="65">Click Filter.</li>
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="66">In the Criteria field, type a value.</li>
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="67">Click OK.</li>
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="68">Click OK.
<ul sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="69">
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="69">Confirm the adjustment is proposed. The amount proposed is discounted to the present value.</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li sourcefile="ProcessDoku/02_SupportProcesses/02_01_Finance/localizations/tasks/adjustment-asset-retirement-obligation-estimate.md" sourcestartlinenumber="70">Click Post.</li>
</ol>
